title: Team for the OOL
body: Hey all, we have a team that is not full yet for the OOL, we have Top and maybe Jungle left, kinda unsure about jungle, and we also have place for 2 subs to join us, so if you're interested into joining our team for the OOL tournament, hmu, ign is JT BBE, tourney starts in 3 days, so we'd like you to contact me asap so i can register our team in, thanks :)
